### Description

Since Angular@13 drop the support of IE11 and differential loading, so do we have a way to enable differential loading for Angular@13?

### Proposed solution

```json
// tsconfig.json
{
  "angularCompilerOptions":{
     "differentialLoading": true
  }
}
```

### Alternatives considered

```json
// tsconfig.json
{
  "angularCompilerOptions":{
     "differentialLoading": true
  }
}
```
